tions will offer some form of peace prayer and pledge to welcome all athletes who seek them, they are readying for possible flareups between those whose countries are at war.\", \"from\": 6312, \"to\": 6509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most denominations\", \"from\": 6322, \"to\": 6340}, {\"ngram\": \"some form\", \"from\": 6352, \"to\": 6361}, {\"ngram\": \"peace prayer\", \"from\": 6365, \"to\": 6377}, {\"ngram\": \"all athletes\", \"from\": 6400, \"to\": 6412}, {\"ngram\": \"possible flareups\", \"from\": 6450, \"to\": 6467}, {\"ngram\": \"whose countries\", \"from\": 6482, \"to\": 6497}, {\"ngram\": \"war\", \"from\": 6505, \"to\": 6508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The geopolitical situation will have an impact on athletes, but the Olympic Games provide the incredible opportunity of meeting the other,\\\" said Lewin, special advisor to the chief Rabbi of France and vice president of the Conference of European Rabbis, who will serve as a Jewish chaplain.\", \"from\": 6511, \"to\": 6802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6702, \"end\": 6708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9994334845570456, \"rank\": 0.0005619822961818131, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 6786, \"end\": 6792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\", \"score\": 0.999999998630301, \"rank\": 1.36962466001187e-09, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The geopolitical situation\", \"from\": 6512, \"to\": 6538}, {\"ngram\": \"an impact\", \"from\": 6549, \"to\": 6558}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 6562, \"to\": 6570}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 6576, \"to\": 6593}, {\"ngram\": \"the incredible opportunity\", \"from\": 6602, \"to\": 6628}, {\"ngram\": \"Lewin\", \"from\": 6657, \"to\": 6662}, {\"ngram\": \"special advisor\", \"from\": 6664, \"to\": 6679}, {\"ngram\": \"the chief Rabbi\", \"from\": 6683, \"to\": 6698}, {\"ngram\": \"vice president\", \"from\": 6713, \"to\": 6727}, {\"ngram\": \"the Conference\", \"from\": 6731, \"to\": 6745}, {\"ngram\": \"European Rabbis\", \"from\": 6749, \"to\": 6764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do worship, not politics,\\\" Benali echoed him.\", \"from\": 6804, \"to\": 6853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"politics\", \"from\": 6824, \"to\": 6832}, {\"ngram\": \"Benali\", \"from\": 6835, \"to\": 6841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will listen and explain we are there to accompany the athletes.\", \"from\": 6854, \"to\": 6921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 6908, \"to\": 6920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not good resources to address geopolitics.\\\"\", \"from\": 6922, \"to\": 6972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good resources\", \"from\": 6933, \"to\": 6947}, {\"ngram\": \"geopolitics\", \"from\": 6959, \"to\": 6970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of that spiritual accompaniment will stem from how each denomination defines the role of health, the human body and thus sports.\", \"from\": 6974, \"to\": 7107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Part\", \"from\": 6974, \"to\": 6978}, {\"ngram\": \"that spiritual accompaniment\", \"from\": 6982, \"to\": 7010}, {\"ngram\": \"each denomination\", \"from\": 7030, \"to\": 7047}, {\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 7056, \"to\": 7064}, {\"ngram\": \"health\", \"from\": 7068, \"to\": 7074}, {\"ngram\": \"the human body\", \"from\": 7076, \"to\": 7090}, {\"ngram\": \"thus sports\", \"from\": 7095, \"to\": 7106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many religious texts describe the body as a temple of the spirit, making it a moral duty to take care of good health.\", \"from\": 7108, \"to\": 7225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many religious texts\", \"fro